 policy that uses the two-phase trial\nsolution's structural insights. We also contrast the optimal signaling policy\nstructure with classical Bayesian persuasion strategies to highlight the impact\nof the signaling constraints on the sender.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 19:31:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Oct 2021 01:12:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 21:23:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-24"}
