cularly precise, we measure a mean apsidal motion constant,\n$\\overline{k_{2}}$, of $ 0.046^{+0.046}_{-0.028}$, which is approximately\n2-$\\sigma$ lower than the theoretical model prediction of 0.150. We explore\npossible causes for this discrepancy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 23:57:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
